<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>netstandard1.2</TargetFramework>
    <Version>1.3.0</Version>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>v1.3.0
Support for empty values and unquoted nulls to act as null queries.

